OL,3,CPolice officer investigated over
OL,4,Calleged use of AI to 'create evidence'
OL,6,FPolice have launched a criminal
OL,7,Finvestigation into an officer from
OL,8,FDerbyshire Police accused of using
OL,9,Fartificial intelligence (AI) to
OL,10,F"create evidential material".
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,13,Fsaid they were working with the force
OL,14,Fto conduct inquiries into the use of
OL,15,FAI by an officer.
OL,17,FAccording to a report in the Financial
OL,18,FTimes, the officer is alleged to have
OL,19,Fused AI to "create evidential material
OL,20,Fin a number of cases".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@\O]{D@LOU|D@UO]
