PN,34302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1781442674
OL,3,CPolice officer investigated over
OL,4,Calleged use of AI to 'create evidence'
OL,6,FThe CPS said they are "engaging with"
OL,7,Fdefence teams and courts which may
OL,8,Fhave been affected by the alleged
OL,9,Fconduct.
OL,11,FA spokesperson from Derbyshire Police
OL,12,Fsaid: "A criminal investigation has
OL,13,Fbeen launched into an allegation of
OL,14,Fperverting the course of justice after
OL,15,Fthe alleged use of AI systems by an
OL,16,Fofficer to create evidential material
OL,17,Fin a number of cases.
OL,26,@nD@WOUnD@eO]tD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1781442674
OL,3,CPolice officer investigated over
OL,4,Calleged use of AI to 'create evidence'
OL,6,F"The force is working closely with the
OL,7,FCrown Prosecution Service in relation
OL,8,Fto any potentially impacted cases,
OL,9,Fhowever, the investigation is in its
OL,10,Fearly stages, so no further details
OL,11,Fare available.
OL,13,F"The officer involved has been removed
OL,14,Ffrom frontline duties, pending the
OL,15,Foutcome of the investigation. No
OL,16,Farrests have been made."
OL,18,FIt comes in the same week that a new
OL,19,Fnational centre for AI in policing,
OL,20,Fcalled PoliceAI, has been launched.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
