CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1781442674
OL,3,CPolice officer investigated over
OL,4,Calleged use of AI to 'create evidence'
OL,6,FAt the launch on Wednesday, PoliceAI
OL,7,Finterim director Alex Murray said:
OL,8,F"Crime and technology are evolving
OL,9,Frapidly.
OL,11,F"Policing must keep pace by adopting
OL,12,FAI responsibly to catch criminals and
OL,13,Fkeep people safe."
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOUuD@RO]
